TV presenter Guy Martin wrote a review of the new Aston Martin Vanquish on the Isle of Man TT course . 
  He claimed he reached speeds of 180mph in a 40mph zone during a test drive of the supercar . 
  The 33-year-old said he pressed the accelerator 'flat to the floor' He said he reached the top speed as he entered the village of Sulby which has a speed limit of 40mph . 
  Police on the island have confirmed they are investigating the claims . 
 